¦In loving memory of Laura Smallwood
08/01/85 - 04/05/19
A loving wife and mummy, 
a beautiful daughter,
sister, niece, aunt and cousin and an eternal friend
forever in our hearts xx

A heart of gold stopped beating,
Two shining eyes at rest,
God broke our hearts to prove,
He only takes the best"¼
®'Oss Oss' Mervyn
for Folk
In memory of Mervyn Vincent and
his beloved wife Jeannie
'United once more'
From all their family and friends
much loved, never forgotten"▒
«In Loving Memory of Justina Clace Alt Moore beloved wife
of Col. "Jim" Moore, whose generous gift of a Holiday Home
enabled her family to enjoy many happy hours at Padstow."Ą
▓In loving memory of
Valerie Irene and Allan, Derek Hurrell of Rochford
who had meny happy times in Padstow.
Sadly missed by their children, grandchildren and all who knew them"Ė
